Package: datadiff
Title: Data Frame Comparison Tools for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Tyler", "Hays", email = "tyhays@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to compare and visualize differences between data frames, including row-by-row and column-wise comparison, context-aware diffing, and HTML report generation for data analysis workflows.
